{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We were there in 1987.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And the cemetery, if I remember correctly, was 156.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And this was a long way away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] For me personally, maybe it wasn't as traumatic as for a grownup, being only 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I found a lot of kids in the surrounding backyards that I got friendly with.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I didn't go to school then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "While we were with them there-- which means the beginning of 1940-- I didn't go into school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My paternal grandparents [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were taken away with an [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They were sent out of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And one sister, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my father's sister, Topcha, blonde, blue-eyed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "She looked like a shiksa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "She didn't look Jewish at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "She could've saved herself if she would have gone away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "She was the only one left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I think that she didn't sleep at home when they came for them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "She must have stayed with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "She was very close with my father and with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "She wasn't married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can I go back again?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came back from that camp in 1939, from the summer camp-- she loved me very much.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She waited for me at the bus station with a, with a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what [NON-ENGLISH] are?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One-horse carriage, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's like a taxi, but that was it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She waited for me there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She picked me up with it, actually brought me home, [NON-ENGLISH] Topcha.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Apparently, she stayed with us because she was left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sent away the whole family, the sister that lived at this house, another younger brother and-- my father had two younger brothers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Wolf was the youngest.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
